In the post, he revealed he has had numerous operations, hormone therapy, chemotherapy and has lost his "silver locks".
Mr Jewson no longer has a stoma bag because the area that has been operated on has healed.
"If my 15 minutes have helped raise awareness, then it's been worthwhile," he said. "Of course, I'm now 'pants man' to all my friends but it's cool."
The original post was shared 250,000 times and viewed by 25m people.
